    <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
  <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #a9a7af; margin: 0;">
    <i><em>Both Beijing and Hong Kong‚Äôs governments have repeatedly rejected international criticism of Lai‚Äôs prosecution. Credits: Reuters</em></i>
